('EM00000985', 'PH00000985', 'POL00001970', '2026-01-14 09:39:50.074', 'INBOUND', 'customer985@email.com', 'support@insurance.com', 'Appeal of claim denial', 'I am writing to formally appeal the denial of my claim CLM-00000985. I believe this decision was made in error. The damage occurred through no fault of my own and is clearly covered under my policy terms. I have attached additional documentation supporting my case. Please review and reconsider this decision.', 'FEEDBACK', 'POSITIVE_FEEDBACK', '-0.4500', 'NEGATIVE', 'MEDIUM', TRUE, '22.50', '2026-02-17 14:29:50.074'),
