('EM00000987', 'PH00000987', 'POL00001974', '2026-01-14 07:59:50.074', 'INBOUND', 'customer987@email.com', 'claims@insurance.com', 'Question about deductible', 'Quick question - if I increase my deductible from $500 to $1000, how much would my premium decrease? Im trying to lower my monthly payments and want to understand my options. Thanks!', 'CANCELLATION', 'CANCEL_POLICY', '0.3700', 'NEUTRAL', 'LOW', TRUE, '23.50', '2026-02-17 14:29:50.074'),
