('EM00000995', 'PH00000995', 'POL00001990', '2026-01-14 01:19:50.074', 'OUTBOUND', 'claims@insurance.com', 'customer995@email.com', 'Thank you for the quick resolution', 'I just wanted to send a quick note to thank your team for the excellent service on my recent claim. Sarah from the claims department was incredibly helpful and professional. The entire process was smooth and the check arrived faster than expected. Its nice to know my insurance company is there when I need them!', 'FEEDBACK', 'POSITIVE_FEEDBACK', '0.9000', 'POSITIVE', 'LOW', FALSE, NULL, '2026-02-17 14:29:50.074'),
