('EM00002000', 'PH00002000', 'POL00004000', '2025-12-10 03:49:50.074', 'OUTBOUND', 'claims@insurance.com', 'customer2000@email.com', 'Thank you for the quick resolution', 'I just wanted to send a quick note to thank your team for the excellent service on my recent claim. Sarah from the claims department was incredibly helpful and professional. The entire process was smooth and the check arrived faster than expected. Its nice to know my insurance company is there when I need them!', 'CLAIMS', 'STATUS_INQUIRY', '0.9000', 'POSITIVE', 'LOW', FALSE, NULL, '2026-02-17 14:29:50.074'),
('EM00002001', 'PH00002001', 'POL00004002', '2025-12-10 02:59:50.074', 'INBOUND', 'customer2001@email.com', 'claims@insurance.com', 'Coverage question for upcoming trip', 'Hi, Im planning a trip to Europe next month and wanted to confirm what coverage I have while traveling abroad. Specifically, does my auto policy cover rental cars in foreign countries? If not, what additional coverage would you recommend? Thanks!', 'CLAIMS', 'FILE_CLAIM', '0.1100', 'NEUTRAL', 'LOW', TRUE, '13.00', '2026-02-17 14:29:50.074'),
('EM00002002', 'PH00002002', 'POL00004004', '2025-12-10 02:09:50.074', 'INBOUND', 'customer2002@email.com', 'support@insurance.com', 'Cancellation request', 'Please cancel my policy effective at the end of this month. I have found coverage elsewhere at a better rate. Please confirm the cancellation and any refund I may be entitled to for the unused premium portion. My policy number is POL-00004004', 'BILLING', 'PAYMENT_ISSUE', '-0.2800', 'NEUTRAL', 'LOW', TRUE, '13.50', '2026-02-17 14:29:50.074'),
